data.name: AboutUsContent
data.value:
The LEO Management System; SPA & Salon was created after years of research in 2018. Our team of founders consister of former salon professionals and some extremely talendted software developers, all with a mission to create software that defeat all the rest in the genre.
This was why LEO was created after about four years of through research and many other details interviews with salon owners. As a result we finally came up with comprehensive software that has only been improved with each passing year.
To touch of our delight, we've managed to gain the trust of several clients who've recommended us to friends and acquaintances establishing us as one of the forerunners in the salon software industry.
